{"tid":2202810,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"在家水耕種菜測試","createTime":"2020-09-15T01:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T00:04:10.000Z","uid":18844,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0b9e1ef66d4e9ada8ff4ea651f420217e5b7cb","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T01:36:18.000Z","msg":"生菜DAY:0 有8格，落種子（每格放1～2粒種）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yqb2j0m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyqb2j0m.png&h=1c0db489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n生菜DAY:4 已經有兩格發左芽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7DzbXM5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7DzbXM5.png&h=15fa9016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qt7drFw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQt7drFw.png&h=91770daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n土炮水種九層塔 （YouTube有個方法叫 Kratky Method)<br />\n浸左水約一星期發晒根，轉落化肥水 (Blue Planet Nutrients BlueMax A&amp;B)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51J0Q7f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51J0Q7f.png&h=25855f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始用左大約 600 ppm TDS<br />\n浸兩日有少部分根發黑<br />\n今日改低啲TDS 約300<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZxQFQ7n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxQFQ7n.png&h=7d2c3502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條野彎左係因為一開始求其掉落個杯仔到<br />\n植物向光+反地心吸力就彎左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二棵九層塔<br />\n岩岩開咗出左兩條根就掉入300 ppm TDS化肥水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yHqZnd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyHqZnd5.png&h=ade6434c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yRGxHec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyRGxHec.png&h=c02bbbd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲九層塔老母一開始係街市買返來就已經好der皮<br />\n係樣衰啲，希望種種下靚仔返<br />\n<br />\n另外order緊HACH 2745425 NO2 NO3 試紙<br />\nfor未來測試 啲生菜 硝酸鹽/亞硝酸鹽 會否超標<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ad507d7d0e73a0a6d27337400bc0f4a1d8ef08","tid":2202810,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:03:01.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4064dfa4cb5b365b5b43da7c23d602e6f9dc6998","tid":2202810,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:03:35.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2aa0a148d25ef40223c86f02b9762612283c7ca5","tid":2202810,"uid":14349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:04:38.000Z","msg":"勁呀， 我都想種下香草。<br />\n<br />\n請教一下，百里香Rosemary 之類是否都可以用水種到?"},{"pid":"453bb0c3de9771501cdc3cc7072635c8b42ba28c","tid":2202810,"uid":33359,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:06:51.000Z","msg":"水耕師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb9a1703c971560d184c3bbba6550c8ab1c1a0f","tid":2202810,"uid":82359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:09:51.000Z","msg":"我like你紙杯個設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但生大啲之後會唔會hold唔住"},{"pid":"8ec861421201ff7391f438818c11948e2d4244c4","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aa0a148d25ef40223c86f02b9762612283c7ca5","tid":2202810,"uid":14349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:04:38.000Z","msg":"勁呀， 我都想種下香草。<br />\n<br />\n請教一下，百里香Rosemary 之類是否都可以用水種到?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:10:32.000Z","msg":"Rosemary 網上講泡水係最易發根<br />\n上面留少少葉做光合作用，下面啲葉去除<br />\n我之前係英國啲hard water都發到<br />\n人地講日日換水喉水會發快啲，我就得閒就換下水咁"},{"pid":"e88c1f53f12dec1e3ba29f9aec65d58c192b7efb","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2aa0a148d25ef40223c86f02b9762612283c7ca5","tid":2202810,"uid":14349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:04:38.000Z","msg":"勁呀， 我都想種下香草。<br />\n<br />\n請教一下，百里香Rosemary 之類是否都可以用水種到?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:15:32.000Z","msg":"之但係我係英國用hard water泡 Thai basil （紅骨九層塔）<br />\n唔知係水定天氣，係唔撚出根的！<br />\n<br />\n跟住我移落泥到，放入小型膠套溫室保濕<br />\n<br />\n九層塔我發現唔可以留太多葉<br />\n我之前係水泡紅骨九層塔（Thai basil）<br />\n留啲葉多少少，空氣唔流通，即刻會生花俾你！（開完花會成棵死左）<br />\n<br />\n解決方法係去除大部分大葉，留細葉<br />\n<br />\n我估香港啲soft water 易發根啲？<br />\n當然唔同品種，我呢隻綠色葉，形狀似Thai basil，一星期左右已經爆好多根"},{"pid":"75125ed15ff788a0e3f328d917a0eb2b1154b98d","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffb9a1703c971560d184c3bbba6550c8ab1c1a0f","tid":2202810,"uid":82359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:09:51.000Z","msg":"我like你紙杯個設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但生大啲之後會唔會hold唔住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"我見啲廢物好似可以利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好大機會hold唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢下面生個叉生大啲頂住<br />\n或者到時DIY個bucket + 陶土粒"},{"pid":"6026525aceaa0c89cea11c6bec957885ef29587b","tid":2202810,"uid":42665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"高質post留名"},{"pid":"ac8695895dc395c862759cc31eec41aa5bb1cc93","tid":2202810,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"岩岩發芽啲葉仔so cute cute <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e919b0b63046f5a9d6757f412e064768666f2a55","tid":2202810,"uid":316329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:57:06.000Z","msg":"水耕多唔多蟲？"},{"pid":"c376c50b0d7ea5211be00165eb3032e294232b77","tid":2202810,"uid":3028,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"m記杯<br />\nblocked<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3278671c50b5da11014fee5cc58e6f45c9b33f24","tid":2202810,"uid":19927,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c376c50b0d7ea5211be00165eb3032e294232b77","tid":2202810,"uid":3028,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"m記杯<br />\nblocked<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:05:14.000Z","msg":"連登仔口講就黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602a46e29d27d256b2e6a0a36da12f55b6d10415","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e919b0b63046f5a9d6757f412e064768666f2a55","tid":2202810,"uid":316329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:57:06.000Z","msg":"水耕多唔多蟲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:11:41.000Z","msg":"呢樣要試下先知, 正常如果無蟲接觸到水應該無事<br />\n我會搵野擋一擋啲可以入到水既位置<br />\n防止蚊入去生蛋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f008458058c1c882e888ffdd852aff3f424c7eb","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c376c50b0d7ea5211be00165eb3032e294232b77","tid":2202810,"uid":3028,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"m記杯<br />\nblocked<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"sorry 之前零晨3-4點肚餓叫的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家作適正常<br />\n多數自煮早訓"},{"pid":"793928268adc86a283ef9ac76d72ed2b621ec8d6","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac8695895dc395c862759cc31eec41aa5bb1cc93","tid":2202810,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"岩岩發芽啲葉仔so cute cute <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"起碼要種一個月先食得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ec54500800eac94ba27ba3c903e3c9092ce9b2","tid":2202810,"uid":172102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"793928268adc86a283ef9ac76d72ed2b621ec8d6","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac8695895dc395c862759cc31eec41aa5bb1cc93","tid":2202810,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"岩岩發芽啲葉仔so cute cute <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"起碼要種一個月先食得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:16:29.000Z","msg":"食咗佢會唔捨得<br />\n我種開啲多肉我好有感情<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf0d9a9a3b0ba263926833d04de9bba71f046ba","tid":2202810,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"送你去火星開發"},{"pid":"63eae9b2f2bda2f8c4adeae3b370fe45c55d8556","tid":2202810,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9ec54500800eac94ba27ba3c903e3c9092ce9b2","tid":2202810,"uid":172102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"793928268adc86a283ef9ac76d72ed2b621ec8d6","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac8695895dc395c862759cc31eec41aa5bb1cc93","tid":2202810,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"岩岩發芽啲葉仔so cute cute <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"起碼要種一個月先食得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:16:29.000Z","msg":"食咗佢會唔捨得<br />\n我種開啲多肉我好有感情<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:25:57.000Z","msg":"多肉唔好食啫"},{"pid":"d22f765a653199872daaff7dc8a7c2a64cec2565","tid":2202810,"uid":296231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:41:09.000Z","msg":"九層塔，rosemary呢d種係泥到自己就會生<br />\n好奇點解樓主要搞咁多野？<br />\n純粹為興趣做實驗？"},{"pid":"caa717d4efaabab723cdaa7b945932e91d7fb3c6","tid":2202810,"uid":370202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n見公司都有幾部水耕菜機<br />\n有時會著燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n種出來啲菜細細棵幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問樓主機種同自製器皿去種有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173c2957dcd5c5feb19eff49e7434bb65f564a0e","tid":2202810,"uid":210558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:02:42.000Z","msg":"屋企有水耕菜機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功種到通菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqf25oJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgqf25oJ.jpg&h=d9f8d629&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27d408a284826f9052ed97f72145e03d4bb2307a","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caa717d4efaabab723cdaa7b945932e91d7fb3c6","tid":2202810,"uid":370202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n見公司都有幾部水耕菜機<br />\n有時會著燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n種出來啲菜細細棵幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問樓主機種同自製器皿去種有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:15:53.000Z","msg":"部機有上下兩層，下層有pump，會punp水去上層再流落下層<br />\nSet 左機械式計時器供電開關個pump<br />\n咁就可以製造水流，補返水去上層，同埋層加少少水中含氧量，有利根部生長<br />\n<br />\n遲啲加算再擴建其他部件掛係窗口上部，中部種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無機器pump水/pump氣<br />\nKratky method 係令到一半根在空氣，一部分在營養液中，咁啲根會生好啲"},{"pid":"87ccc094d6e579831f6e72cb4c9f8ce131c39eaa","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"173c2957dcd5c5feb19eff49e7434bb65f564a0e","tid":2202810,"uid":210558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:02:42.000Z","msg":"屋企有水耕菜機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功種到通菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqf25oJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgqf25oJ.jpg&h=d9f8d629&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"巴打勁，你就是成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dde9d1901d459632b13a2c15cef832324d2582","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d22f765a653199872daaff7dc8a7c2a64cec2565","tid":2202810,"uid":296231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:41:09.000Z","msg":"九層塔，rosemary呢d種係泥到自己就會生<br />\n好奇點解樓主要搞咁多野？<br />\n純粹為興趣做實驗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"想做垂直種菜，上，中部都掛容器種植，又可以擋下太陽又無咁熱<br />\n但想先測試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6195121e724ced7ea7b6c0905ddd63a7770678c","tid":2202810,"uid":259877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"之前玩過下，種左幾年之後唔知做乜9 就種唔到 菜"},{"pid":"8fe6fe54d7052c1f70f0d1ed0a8d904711b459a9","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6195121e724ced7ea7b6c0905ddd63a7770678c","tid":2202810,"uid":259877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"