，好唔好吖～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f3e821229a22c5d58f97a78e704cb7fc23bc97","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18d44ce0b17121b53ea01f90b5474f8c127ec041","tid":2202810,"uid":111019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:27:03.000Z","msg":"用個化學營養水會唔會食死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"普遍來講水耕「有機會」導致作物裏面既 硝酸鹽 / 亞硝酸鹽 (氮肥) 偏高<br />\n原因係營養液過高氮肥 / 光照不足, 氮肥 supply &gt;&gt;&gt; 植物使用 demand<br />\n解決方法係:<br />\n臨收成前個一日, 將營養液換成 清水 / 低濃度營養液, 曬夠太陽就應該OK<br />\n由於都驚呢個常見問題, 所以都會買試紙, 第日test<br />\n例子: <a href=\"http://www.producegreen.org.hk/topic_02_02.html#10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.producegreen.org.hk%2Ftopic_02_02.html%2310&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=0d964d8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.producegreen.org.hk/topic_02_02.html#10</a>"},{"pid":"14c428ef43d29d54662e6a302742717d9b6e1707","tid":2202810,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"deffcf9bbc274a54d20ed652658237c0fe2ce186","tid":2202810,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:28:57.000Z","msg":"支持樓豬，但唔好再幫襯中資M記喇，好唔好吖～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:35:44.000Z","msg":"放心, 減肥, 唔食垃圾了, sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋而家都係自煮生活了"}]}